---
title: Lemony Chicken Tender Piccata with Capers and Linguine
description: In tonight's take on a classic piccata, chicken tenders are floured and pan-fried until deliciously golden, then draped in a silky sauce peppered with briny capers and hints of tart lemon. You'll be licking the bowl clean to catch every last drop!
